Your guide to optimal results

















Hello Himanshi,











We&#39;re excited to see you&#39;ve created a Gemini API key and are eager to help you bring your AI ideas to life. When you&#39;re ready to make your first API call, consider these helpful tips:


































Craft clear and concise prompts




Be specific about the desired output and format.








































Use examples to guide the model




Illustrate the type of response you&#39;re looking for.








































Experiment with different phrasing and keywords




Iterate to refine your prompts and achieve better results.








































For Gemini models




Utilize the full range of input modalities (text, images, video, and audio) and tailor your prompts accordingly.


































